                    <Property Name="Text" >GAME RULES
----------------
THE GOAL OF THE GAME IS 
TO DODGE THE BLOCKS AND
OTHER ENEMY OBJECTS. IF
YOU HIT A BLOCK YOU WILL
DRIVE ON BUT LOSE ENERGY.
WHEN YOUR ENERGY IS ZERO
YOU LOSE A LIFE. WHEN
YOUR LIFES ARE ZERO
THE GAME IS OVER.

THERE ARE SEVERAL OBJECTS
IN THE LEVELS YOU CAN PICK
UP. THE BRIGHT ONES HAVE
NO EFFECT ON THE GAME BUT
GIVE LOW POINTS. THE DARK
ONES GIVE MANY POINTS BUT
THERE MAY BE A SURPRISE YOU
WON'T LIKE...

CONTROLS
----------------
MOVE THE PLAYER
-> ARROW KEYS ON KEYBOARD

SHOW / HIDE INFORMATION
-> F1

WIREFRAME / POLYGON MODE
-> F2 / F3

PAUSE / IN GAME MENU
-> P / ESC

                    </Property>
